Fries and German Sausage Crispy golden fries topped with caramelized onions and sliced German-style sausage braised in our Oktoberfest lager, finished with a drizzle of our house-made curry ketchup and a sprinkle of fresh chives. Try with a pint of Clear Creek Pale Ale

Pork Cutlets Two crispy breaded pork cutlets, pan-seared and smothered in a rich mushroom hunter sauce, served with garlic mashed potatoes and tender braised red cabbage. Try with a pint of Ridgetop Red

Beer-Basted German Sausage A juicy German-style bratwurst, braised in our Oktoberfest lager, flame-grilled, and tucked into a rustic bun. Topped with sauerkraut and our Panther Lake Porter honey mustard, and served with German potato salad. Try with a pint of Oktoberfest Lager

Bavarian Pork Roast Rich pork shoulder, seasoned with traditional German spices and slow roasted with our Oktoberfest lager until fork-tender, then smothered in savory onion gravy. Served with braised red cabbage and fresh-made sptzle sauted in brown butter. Try with a pint of Bavarian Hefeweizen

Bavarian Pizza Caramelized sweet onions, smoky bacon, and a touch of Cambozola a creamy, triple-cream blue cheese baked on our traditional pizza crust. Finished with parmesan and fresh parsley. Try with a pint of Tropic Haze IPA
